{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778431075970,"sessionID":"ses_1ed3f6926ffeBLriFMTumDj8z2","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_mz6YuPQ6rUxWeJmIcjMhk0nv","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json","offset":1,"limit":2000},"output":"<path>/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"body\": \"- [x] Add EC:1.1.1.358 2-dehydropantolactone reductase as exactMatch to GO:0036441 2-dehydropantolactone reductase activity\\n- [x] Add/make EC:1.17.3.2 broadMatch xref on GO:0070675 hypoxanthine oxidase activity and GO:0004855 xanthine oxidase activity\\n- [x] Also, add [RHEA:68012](https://www.rhea-db.org/rhea/68012) as exactMatch xref on GO:0070675 hypoxanthine oxidase activity, and use as def xref.\\n- [x] Add EC:1.14.14.24 to GO:0030343 vitamin D3 25-hydroxylase activity (and change name to 'vitamin D 25-hydroxylase activity' to match EC and other similar GO terms)\",\n3:   \"comments\": [],\n4:   \"title\": \"Missing EC/RHEA xrefs to add to oxidoreductase activity GO terms\",\n5:   \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31962\"\n6: }\n\n(End of file - total 6 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"body\": \"- [x] Add EC:1.1.1.358 2-dehydropantolactone reductase as exactMatch to GO:0036441 2-dehydropantolactone reductase activity\\n- [x] Add/make EC:1.17.3.2 broadMatch xref on GO:0070675 hypoxanthine oxidase activity and GO:0004855 xanthine oxidase activity\\n- [x] Also, add [RHEA:68012](https://www.rhea-db.org/rhea/68012) as exactMatch xref on GO:0070675 hypoxanthine oxidase activity, and use as def xref.\\n- [x] Add EC:1.14.14.24 to GO:0030343 vitamin D3 25-hydroxylase activity (and change name to 'vitamin D 25-hydroxylase activity' to match EC and other similar GO terms)\",\n  \"comments\": [],\n  \"title\": \"Missing EC/RHEA xrefs to add to oxidoreductase activity GO terms\",\n  \"ur